878
00:42:06,920 --> 00:42:08,280
I asked her for some help.

879
00:42:09,440 --> 00:42:10,480
Good.

880
00:42:10,560 --> 00:42:11,800
In relationships,

881
00:42:11,880 --> 00:42:14,600
