906
00:43:16,680 --> 00:43:18,240
As long as we persevere,

907
00:43:19,120 --> 00:43:20,360
our time will come.

908
00:43:21,600 --> 00:43:23,400
Why does it sound like

909
00:43:23,480 --> 00:43:25,520
